22%3A%22%3Cp%3EUnion%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%20on%20Saturday%20launched%20the%20third%20part%20of%20the%20BJP%20manifesto%20for%20the%20upcoming%20Delhi%20Assembly%20elections%2C%20scheduled%20for%20February%205.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20party%20has%20announced%20several%20promises%2C%20ranging%20from%20granting%20ownership%20rights%20to%20people%20in%20refugee%20colonies%20to%20reopening%2013%2C000%20sealed%20shops%20in%20the%20national%20capital.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAddressing%20the%20event%2C%20Amit%20Shah%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BModi%20ji%20has%20announced%20the%20granting%20of%20ownership%20rights%20to%20more%20than%201%2C700%20unauthorized%20colonies.%20Previously%2C%20these%20colonies%20did%20not%20have%20permission%20for%20construction%2C%20buying%2C%20or%20selling.%20Now%2C%20by%20granting%20them%20full%20ownership%20rights%20and%20aligning%20with%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Housing's%20regulations%20and%20Delhi's%20by-laws%2C%20we%20will%20give%20them%20the%20right%20to%20construct%20and%20sell.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B13%2C000%20shops%20in%20Delhi%20are%20sealed%2C%20and%20we%20have%20worked%20with%20lawyers%20to%20find%20a%20legal%20path%20to%20reopen%20them.%20We%20will%20create%20a%20judicial%20authority%20and%20reopen%20these%20shops%20within%20six%20months%20to%20resume%20operations.%20Refugee%20colonies%20that%20have%20been%20established%20since%201947%2C%20such%20as%20Rajendra%20Nagar%2C%20Lajpat%20Nagar%2C%20and%20Kingsway%20Camp%2C%20currently%20have%20people%20on%20lease%3B%20they%20cannot%20sell%20or%20buy%20the%20land.%20We%20will%20grant%20ownership%20rights%20to%20all%20these%20refugees%20who%20have%20land%20on%20lease%20in%20these%20colonies%20in%20the%20first%20Cabinet%20meeting%2C%26quot%3B%20Shah%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Home%20Minister%20also%20announced%20the%20establishment%20of%20a%20Workers%20Welfare%20Board%20in%20Delhi%2C%20which%20will%20ensure%20that%20all%20workers%20have%20life%20insurance%20coverage%20of%20up%20to%2010%20lakh%20and%20accident%20insurance%20of%20up%20to%205%20lakh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20will%20apply%20the%20same%20formula%20for%20textile%20workers.%20We%20will%20provide%20Rs%2010%2C000%20as%20assistance%20to%20workers%2C%20and%20for%20registered%20workers%2C%20we%20will%20offer%20loans%20up%20to%203%20lakh%20to%20enhance%20skills%20and%20businesses%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20further%20highlighted%20that%20the%20BJP%20would%20provide%2050%2C000%20government%20jobs%20to%20the%20youth%20of%20Delhi%20without%20any%20corruption.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnd%20by%20creating%2020%20lakh%20self-employment%20opportunities%2C%20we%20will%20help%20the%20youth%20find%20employment.%20Through%20an%20investment%20of%2020%2C000%20crore%2C%20we%20will%20develop%20an%20integrated%20public%20transport%20network%20and%20convert%2013%2C000%20buses%20into%20electric%20buses%2C%20making%20Delhi%20a%20100%25%20electric%20bus%20city%20under%20the%20BJP%20government%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20underlined%20that%20to%20promote%20tourism%2C%20they%20will%20collaborate%20with%20the%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20and%20Haryana%20governments%20to%20create%20a%20Mahabharata%20corridor.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20will%20develop%20the%20Yamuna%20Riverfront%2C%20similar%20to%20the%20Sabarmati%20Riverfront.%20I%20would%20like%20to%20invite%20Kejriwal%20to%20join%20us%20after%203%20years%20of%20our%20government%20to%20take%20a%20dip%20in%20the%20Yamuna%20with%20his%20family.%20We%20will%20end%20manual%20scavenging%20100%25%20and%20eliminate%20this%20inhumane%20practice%20completely%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Union%20Home%20Minister%20also%20recalled%20the%20BJP's%20promises%20from%20its%20earlier%20two%20manifestos.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BFor%20every%20pregnant%20woman%2C%20we%20will%20provide%20financial%20assistance%20of%20Rs%2012%2C000%20and%20give%20six%20nutrition%20kits.%20LPG%20cylinders%20will%20be%20available%20for%20Rs%20500%2C%20and%20BJP%20will%20provide%20one%20free%20LPG%20cylinder%20to%20every%20sister%20on%20Holi%20and%20Diwali.%20Under%20the%20Ayushman%20Bharat%20scheme%2C%20we%20will%20provide%20free%20treatment%20up%20to%205%20lakh%20in%20the%20first%20Cabinet%20meeting%20to%20every%20poor%20person.%20Any%20treatment%20beyond%205%20lakh%20will%20be%20covered%20by%20the%20Delhi%20government%2C%20ensuring%20that%20every%20poor%20person%20in%20Delhi%20receives%20treatment%20up%20to%2010%20lakh%20at%20no%20cost%2C%20even%20at%20major%20hospitals.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20mentioned%20that%20the%20BJP%20government%20would%20increase%20the%20pension%20for%20senior%20citizens%20from%20Rs%202%2C000%20to%20Rs%202%2C500%20per%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20women's%20welfare%2C%20we%20will%20increase%20the%20pension%20for%20widows%20and%20destitute%20women%20from%202%2C500%20Rs%20to%203%2C000%20Rs%20per%20month.%20We%20will%20establish%20Atal%20Canteens%20in%20JJ%20Clusters%2C%20providing%20nutritious%20meals%20for%20just%20Rs%205%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20will%20give%20a%20corruption-free%20and%20transparent%20state%20government.%20Scheduled%20caste%20and%20scheduled%20tribe%20students%20will%20receive%201%2C000%20Rs%20per%20month%20under%20the%20Ambedkar%20Stipend%20Scheme.%20Auto%20and%20taxi%20drivers%20will%20receive%2010%20lakh%20life%20insurance%20and%205%20lakh%20accident%20insurance.%20A%20welfare%20board%20will%20be%20set%20up%20for%20domestic%20workers%2C%20and%20we%20will%20provide%20six%20months%20of%20paid%20maternity%20leave%20to%20mothers.%20We%20will%20double%20the%20PM%20Swanidhi%20scheme%20and%20provide%20financial%20aid%20to%20street%20vendors%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Delhi%20assembly%20elections%20will%20take%20place%20in%20a%20single%20phase%20on%20February%205.%20The%20counting%20of%20votes%20will%20happen%20on%20February%208.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20three-way%20contest%20is%20expected%20in%20Delhi%20between%20the%20ruling%20AAP%2C%20BJP%2C%20and%20Congress.%20AAP%20dominated%20the%202020%20assembly%20elections%20by%20winning%2062%20out%20of%2070%20seats%2C%20while%20the%20BJP%20secured%20eight%20seats.%20Congress%2C%20which%20was%20in%20power%20for%2015%20consecutive%20years%20in%20Delhi%2C%20has%20suffered%20setbacks%20in%20the%20last%20two%20assembly%20elections%20and%20has%20failed%20to%20win%20any%20seat.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1737805560000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-01%2F73pjufrg_bjp-poll-manifesto-delhi-elections_625x300_25_January_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdelhi-assembly-elections-2025-bjp-manifesto-amit-shah-refugee-colonies-reopening-of-sealed-shops-jobs-7556891%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Union%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%20on%20Saturday%20launched%20the%20third%20part%20of%20the%20BJP%20manifesto%20for%20the%20upcoming%20Delhi%20Assembly%20elections%2C%20scheduled%20for%20February%205.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdelhi-assembly-elections-2025-bjp-manifesto-amit-shah-refugee-colonies-reopening-of-sealed-shops-jobs-7556891%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Coldplay%20Ahmedabad%20concert%3A%20State%20Police%20deploys%203800%20personnel%2C%20NSG%2C%20bomb%20squad%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1737805556000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-117553926%2Cimgsize-50562.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fenglish%2Fmusic%2Fnews%2Fcoldplay-ahmedabad-con