.%20The%20left-arm%20pacer%20starred%20as%20India%20ended%20their%20wait%20for%20a%20major%20ICC%20trophy%20win%20with%20victory%20in%20the%20ICC%20Men's%20T20%20World%20Cup%202024%20in%20the%20Caribbean%20and%20USA%20back%20in%20June%2C%20and%20has%20gone%20on%20to%20cement%20his%20reputation%20as%20one%20of%20the%20leading%20powerplay%20and%20death%20bowlers%20in%20the%20game.%20The%2025-year-old%20has%20long%20been%20tipped%20for%20the%20top%2C%20and%20India%20put%20a%20great%20deal%20of%20faith%20in%20his%20ability%20since%20making%20his%20full%20international%20debut%20in%202022.%20And%202024%20was%20the%20year%20when%20Arshdeep%20fully%20established%20himself%20as%20a%20world-class%20bowler%20in%20T20%20International%20cricket%2C%20taking%20bucket-loads%20of%20wickets%20with%20the%20new%20ball%20and%20proving%20to%20be%20consistently%20economical%20at%20the%20death%20on%20a%20variety%20of%20surfaces.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArshdeep%20was%20the%20leading%20Indian%20wicket-taker%20in%20T20Is%20in%20the%20year%2C%20bagging%2036%20wickets%20in%20just%2018%20games.%20He%20played%20a%20huge%20part%20in%20steering%20India%20to%20the%20title%20at%20the%20ICC%20Men's%20T20%20World%20Cup%20and%20stepped%20up%20as%20leader%20of%20the%20attack%20as%20the%20selectors%20built%20a%20new%20era%20for%20the%20T20%20squad%20following%20the%20triumph%20in%20the%20Caribbean.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnly%20four%20players%20in%20the%20world%20took%20more%20T20I%20wickets%20than%20Arshdeep%20in%20the%20calendar%20year%20-%20Saudi%20Arabia's%20Usman%20Najeeb%20(38)%2C%20Sri%20Lanka's%20Wanindu%20Hasaranga%20(38)%2C%20UAE's%20Junaid%20Siddique%20(40)%20and%20Hong%20Kong's%20Ehsan%20Khan%20(46)%20-%20with%20all%20four%20playing%20more%20matches.%20Of%20those%20bowlers%2C%20only%20Hasaranga%20featured%20for%20a%20full-member%20nation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArshdeep%20took%20his%20wickets%20at%20an%20average%20of%20just%2015.31%20and%2C%20despite%20predominantly%20bowling%20in%20the%20powerplay%20and%20death%20overs%2C%20finished%20the%20year%20with%20an%20economy%20rate%20of%207.49.%20He%20was%20a%20constant%20wicket-taking%20threat%2C%20taking%20his%20wickets%20at%20a%20strike%20rate%20of%2010.80.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArshdeep%20had%20a%20number%20of%20impressive%20displays%20in%20the%20year%2C%20not%20least%20when%20he%20ripped%20through%20the%20USA%20in%20New%20York%20during%20the%20T20%20World%20Cup%20group%20stage%2C%20bagging%20remarkable%20returns%20of%204%2F9%20in%20his%20four%20overs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20Arshdeep's%20most%20significant%20performance%20of%20the%20year%20came%20on%20the%20biggest%20stage%20of%20all%2C%20as%20he%20played%20a%20huge%20part%20in%20helping%20India%20successfully%20defend%20their%20total%20of%20176%20in%20the%20World%20Cup%20final%20in%20Barbados.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20part%20of%20a%20pace%20trio%20with%20Jasprit%20Bumrah%20and%20Hardik%20Pandya%20that%20effectively%20won%20the%20game%20for%20India%2C%20Arshdeep's%20terrific%20figures%20of%202%2F20%20from%20four%20overs%20only%20tell%20part%20of%20the%20story.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExcellent%20with%20the%20new%20ball%20up%20top%2C%20Arshdeep%20struck%20in%20the%20powerplay%20to%20have%20the%20dangerous%20South%20African%20skipper%20Aiden%20Markram%20caught%20behind%20in%20just%20the%20third%20over.%20And%20when%20India%20were%20in%20need%20of%20a%20wicket%20in%20the%20middle%20overs%20it%20was%20Arshdeep%20that%20provided%20the%20breakthrough%2C%20dismissing%20a%20set%20Quinton%20de%20Kock%20when%20the%20Proteas%20looked%20to%20be%20in%20control%20of%20the%20chase.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia's%20collective%20effort%20at%20the%20death%20was%20astonishing%20as%20South%20Africa%20pulled%20up%20seven%20runs%20short%20of%20their%20target%2C%20and%20Arshdeep%20played%20a%20huge%20role%20in%20that%2C%20returning%20to%20the%20attack%20to%20bowl%20the%20penultimate%20over%20with%20South%20Africa%20requiring%2020%20from%2012%20deliveries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArshdeep%20deliver