ing%20revenue%2C%20and%20the%20success%20of%20high%20profile%20events%20and%20digital%20initiatives.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20quarter%2C%20NDTV%20made%20significant%20strides%20in%20expanding%20its%20content%20offerings%20and%20global%20reach%20with%20the%20launch%20of%20NDTV%20World%2C%20a%20global%20news%20platform%20designed%20to%20serve%20the%20diverse%20diaspora%20around%3Cbr%3E%5Cnthe%20globe.%20The%20platform%20offers%20high-quality%20news%2C%20in-depth%20analysis%2C%20and%20programming%20tailored%20to%20global%20audiences%2C%20while%20bringing%20an%20Asian%20and%20Indian%20perspective%20to%20international%20markets.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20commemorate%20this%20landmark%20launch%2C%20NDTV%20hosted%20the%20NDTV%20World%20Summit%2C%20where%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20officially%20launched%20NDTV%20World.%20This%20prestigious%20international%20event%20brought%20together%20some%20of%20the%20world's%20most%20influential%20thought%20leaders%2C%20including%20Prime%20Minister%20of%20Bhutan%20Dasho%20Tshering%20Tobgay%2C%20former%20British%20Prime%20Minister%20Lord%20David%20Cameron%2C%20legendary%20investor%20Mark%20Mobius%2C%20telecom%20magnate%20Sunil%20Bharti%20Mittal%2C%20YouTuber%20NAS%20Daily%2C%20and%20many%20other%20key%20global%20figures.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20quarter%20also%20featured%20high%20impact%20coverage%20of%20Maharashtra%20elections%2C%20US%20elections%20and%20several%20signature%20NDTV%20events%20across%20the%20country%2C%20including%20the%20prestigious%20NDTV%20Indian%20of%20the%20Year%2C%20the%20NDTV%20Auto%20Conclave%2C%20Emerging%20Business%20Conclave%20and%20Real%20Estate%20Conclave.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20events%20attracted%20top%20political%20figures%2C%20industry%20leaders%2C%20celebrities%2C%20and%20influencers%2C%20strengthening%20NDTV's%20position%20as%20a%20major%20player%20in%20the%20events%20and%20content%20space.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20key%20highlight%20this%20quarter%20was%20NDTV's%