26quot%3B%20and%20becoming%20a%20place%20that's%20%26quot%3Bnot%20for%20Puerto%20Ricans.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f38c7f69-e979-4f77-8682-d4fd0595397d%5C%22%3ETempered%20optimism%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20%26quot%3BLo%20Que%20Pas%C3%B3%20a%20Hawaii%2C%26quot%3B%20Bunny%20calls%20on%20Puerto%20Ricans%20to%20retain%20their%20flag%20and%20not%20forget%20their%20roots.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20a%20stark%20warning%2C%20but%20in%20%26quot%3Bsubverting%20the%20narrative%26quot%3B%20that%20the%20island%20should%20aspire%20to%20be%20like%20Hawaii%2C%20Net%20said%20it%20offers%20hope%20and%20pride%20to%20Puerto%20Ricans%20who%20have%20grappled%20with%20a%20%26quot%3Bnagging%20feeling%20that%20nothing%20we%20do%20is%20ever%20good%20enough.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22bad%20bunny%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5d35f4ad36e03c070b57638c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222667%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EBad%20Bunny%20holds%20a%20Puerto%20Rican%20flag%20in%20a%20demonstration%20calling%20for%20Gov.%20Ricardo%20Rossell%C3%B3's%20resignation%20in%20San%20Juan%2C%20Puerto%20Rico%20in%20July%202019.%3Cp%3EERIC%20ROJAS%2FAFP%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ERivera-Rideau%20said%20the%20song%20also%20captures%20the%20political%20spirit%20of%20a%20new%20generation%20of%20Puerto%20Ricans%2C%20who%2C%20like%20Bunny%2C%20grew%20up%20seeing%20the%20island's%20problems%20mount%20and%20now%20want%20change.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHis%20concerns%20about%20electricity%20and%20infrastructure%2C%20gentrification%2C%20tourism%2C%20the%20economy%2C%20opportunities%2C%20growth%20for%20the%20future%20%E2%80%94%20those%20are%20concerns%20that%20many%20Puerto%20Ricans%20have%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20recent%20years%2C%20events%20like%20the%20ousting%20of%20the%20island's%20former%20governor%20Ricardo%20Rossell%C3%B3%20after%20widespread%20protests%20have%20shown%20that%20%26quot%3Byoung%20adults%20are%20really%20energized%2C%26quot%3B%20Rivera-Rideau%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Bad%20Bunny%20performs%20during%20his%20Most%20Wanted%20Tour%20at%20Coliseo%20de%20Puerto%20Rico%20Jos%C3%A9%20Miguel%20Agrelot%20on%20June%207%2C%202024%2C%20in%20San%20Juan%2C%20Puerto%20Rico.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6786568350dfd88e193e319d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22853%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EBad%20Bunny's%20seventh%20album%20voices%20his%20fears%20about%20the%20future%20of%20Puerto%20Rico.%3Cp%3EGladys%20Vega%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20%26quot%3BMarketing%20Puerto%20Rico%2C%26quot%3B%20Bunny%20runs%20a%20risk%20of%20attracting%20more%20mainlanders%2C%20people%20who%20listen%20to%20the%20music%20simply%20because%20they%20find%20it%20%26quot%3Bexotic%26quot%3B%20and%20catchy%2C%20Nev%C3%A1rez%20Ara%C3%BAjo%20cautioned.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20for%20many%20young%20Puerto%20Ricans%2C%20%26quot%3BDebir%20Tirar%20Mas%20Fotos%26quot%3B%20is%20%26quot%3Bthe%20closest%20they%20will%20get%20to%20voicing%20those%20fears%20and%20those%20anxieties%26quot%3B%20about%20the%20island's%20future%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20TikTok%20users%20have%20taken%20to%20posting%20photos%20and%20videos%20of%20people%20and%20places%20they've%20lost%2C%20set%20to%20the%20album's%20title%20track%2C%20indicating%20that%20Bunny's%20music%20is%20resonating%20on%20the%20island%20and%20further%20afield.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMany%20of%20these%20songs%20are%20pointing%20out%20the%20story%20of%20displacement%2C%26quot%3B%20Rodriquez-Silva%20said.%20%26quot%3BThat%20is%20something%20that%20is%20so%20real%20to%20many%20of%20us%20today.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbad-bunny-new-album-puerto-r