C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Fyemens-houthi-rebels-unilaterally-release-153-war-detainees-red-cross-says%2Farticleshow%2F117552072.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Fyemens-houthi-rebels-unilaterally-release-153-war-detainees-red-cross-says%2Famp_articleshow%2F117552072.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Fyemens-houthi-rebels-unilaterally-release-153-war-detainees-red-cross-says%2Famp_articleshow%2F117552072.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Budget%202025%3A%20What%20Changes%20Do%20Economists%20Suggest%20For%20Salaried%20Taxpayers%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EEvery%20Budget%20season%2C%20the%20most-asked%20question%20remains%20the%20same%20-%20does%20it%20have%20anything%20for%20the%20salaried%20class%3F%20With%20Finance%20Minister%20Nirmala%20Sitharaman%20set%20to%20present%20Budget%202025-26%20on%20February%201%2C%20the%20salaried%20class%20is%20again%20looking%20out%20if%20the%20government%20has%20any%20plans%20to%20reduce%20their%20financial%20burden.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEconomists%20have%20suggested%20that%20the%20government%20this%20time%20offer%20a%20higher%20tax%20exemption%20limit%20and%20an%20increased%20standard%20deduction%20under%20the%20new%20tax%20regime%2C%20which%20would%20benefit%20a%20lot%20of%20taxpayers.%20In%20the%20last%20Budget%2C%20the%20standard%20deduction%20was%20increased%20to%20Rs%2075%2C000%20from%20Rs%2050%2C000%20while%20the%20exemption%20limit%20stands%20at%20Rs%203%20lakh%20under%20the%20new%20regime.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20economists%20also%20hinted%20at%20tax%20benefits%20for%20electric%20vehicles%2C%20boosting%20the%20housing%20sector%2C%20and%20easing%20the%20purchase%20and%20sale%20of%20real%20estate%20by%20Non-Residential%20Indians%20(NRIs).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDeepika%20Mathur%2C%20Director%20at%20Deloitte%20India%2C%20said%20that%20if%20the%20government%20plans%20to%20offer%20any%20relief%20to%20the%20salaried%20class%20at%20all%2C%20it%20may%20benefit%20only%20those%20under%20the%20new%20regime.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20really%20do%20not%20expect%20any%20changes%20in%20the%20old%20tax%20regime.%20However%2C%20I%20do%20expect%20a%20further%20increase%20in%20the%20standard%20deduction%20in%20the%20new%20tax%20regime.%20Whatever%20changes%20will%20happen%2C%20whether%20an%20increase%20in%20standard%20deduction%20or%20a%20change%20in%20tax%20rate%20or%20slab%20if%20at%20all%20or%20enhancement%20of%20basic%20exemption%20limit%2C%20I%20expect%20for%20it%20to%20happen%20in%20the%20new%20tax%20regime%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20regime%20simplifies%20tax%20filing%20and%20offers%20lower%20tax%20rates%2C%20but%20unlike%20the%20old%20regime%2C%20it%20does%20not%20offer%20deductions.%20On%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20the%20old%20regime%20offers%20a%20slew%20of%20deductions%20but%20also%20comes%20with%20higher%20rates.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20inflation%20eating%20away%20the%20worth%20of%20money%2C%20consumers%20are%20also%20keen%20on%20efforts%20that%20would%20increase%20the%20purchasing%20powers%20of%20the%20middle%20class.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWeighing%20in%2C%20Sanchita%20Mukherji%2C%20Senior%20Business%20Economist%20and%20Managing%20Partner%20at%20'Talk%20The%20Walk'%2C%20pointed%20out%20that%20salaried%20individuals%20are%20taxed%20disproportionately.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20India%2C%20the%20middle-class%20salaried%20individuals%20pay%20a%20disproportionately%20high%20personal%20income%20tax%20as%20salaries%20are%20taxed%20far%20more%20easily%20than%20any%20other%20kind%20of%20income.%20The%20complaint%20is%20that%20the%20middle%20class%2C%20which%20first%20pays%20tax%20from%20income%2C%20are%20taxed%20again%20while%20spending%20post-tax%20income%20and%20capital%20gains%20from%20the%20sale%20of%20shares%20and%20property%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20key%20challenge%20that%20Ms%20Mathur%20believes%20the%20government%20should%20address%20in%20this%20year's%20Budget%20is%20facilitating%20tax%20payments%20from%20overseas%20bank%20accounts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20are%20a%20lot%20of%20people%20who%20are%20overseas%2C%20they%20are%20foreign%20nationals%2C%20Indians%20or%20Non-Resident%20Indians%2C%20who%20may%20have%20worked%20in%20the%20past%20or%20are%20overseas%20and%20have%20investment%20income%20in%20India.%20The%20payments%20can%20be%20made%20for%20taxes%20only%20from%20an%20Indian%20bank%20account.%20Sometimes%20that's%20a%20challenge%2C%20so%20tax%20payments%20should%20be%20facilitated%20from%20overseas%20bank%20accounts%20because%20the%20government%20is%20concerned%20with%20having%20the%20tax%20payout%20without%20many%20compliance%20issues.%20Therefore%2C%20it%20should%20not%20be%20relevant%20where%20the%20payment%20is%20coming%20from%2C%20whether%20it%20is%20an%20Indian%20bank%20account%20or%20an%20overseas%20bank%20account%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20these%20are%20proposed%20measures%2C%20the%20spotlight%20is%20on%20whether%20February%201%20will%20transform%20the%20taxation%20landscape%20in%20India%20altogether%20or%20will%20the%20middle%20class%20be%20left%20craving%20for%20more%20change.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1737801180000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-01%2F8ponno68_budget-2025_625x300_22_January_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbudget-2025-what-changes-do-economists-suggest-for-salaried-taxpayers-7556365%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22With%20Finance%20Minister%20Nirmala%20Sitharaman%20set%20to%20present%20Union%20Budget%202025-26%20on%20February%201%2C%20the%20salaried%20class%20is%20again%20looking%20out%20if%20the%20government%20has%20any%20plans%20to%20reduce%20their%20financial%20burden.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2