0Bharat's%20Successful%20Trial%20Run%20On%20World's%20Highest%20Rail%20Bridge%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20boost%20to%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir's%20rail%20connectivity%2C%20the%20India%20Railways%20on%20Saturday%20successfully%20conducted%20the%20first%20trial%20run%20of%20the%20specially%20designed%20Vande%20Bharat%20Express%20train.%20The%20train%2C%20which%20travelled%20from%20Shri%20Mata%20Vaishno%20Devi%20Katra%20(SVDK)%20railway%20station%20to%20Srinagar%20railway%20station%2C%20passed%20through%20the%20Chenab%20bridge%20-%20the%20world's%20highest%20rail%20bridge.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20ran%20through%20Anji%20Khad%20bridge%20-%20which%20is%20India's%20first%20cable-stayed%20railway%20bridge.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20train%20briefly%20halted%20at%20Jammu%20around%2011%3A30%20am%20where%20it%20was%20welcomed%20with%20slogans%20and%20praises%20for%20the%20Indian%20Railways.%20It%20then%20moved%20to%20the%20next%20Budgam%20station%20to%20complete%20its%20trial%20run.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECommercial%20operations%20of%20the%20train%20are%20set%20to%20begin%20soon%2C%20with%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20expected%20to%20flag%20off%20the%20first%20journey%20from%20Katra.%20The%20date%20of%20the%20flagging-off%20ceremony%20is%20yet%20to%20be%20announced.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ESpecial%20features%20of%20the%20train%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Vande%20Bharat%20train%20is%20designed%20to%20operate%20seamlessly%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir's%20challenging%20winter%20conditions%20and%20has%20special%20climate-related%20features.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECompared%20to%20the%20other%20Vande%20Bharat%20Express%20trains%20running%20in%20different%20parts%20of%20the%20country%2C%20this%20train%20has%20several%20additional%20features%20to%20meet%20operational%20challenges%20and%20passengers'%20needs.%20It%20includes%20advanced%20heating%20systems%20that%20prevent%20the%20freezing%20of%20water%20and%20bio-toilet%20tanks%2C%20provide%20warm%20air%20for%20the%20vacuum%20system%2C%20and%20ensure%20optimal%20functioning%20of%20the%20air-brake%20system%20for%20smooth%20operations%20even%20in%20sub-zero%20temperatures.%20The%20train%20also%20features%20embedded%20heating%20elements%20in%20the%20windshield%20to%20automatically%20defrost%20the%20driver's%20front%20lookout%20glass%2C%20ensuring%20clear%20visibility%20in%20harsh%20winter%20conditions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApart%20from%20these%2C%20the%20train%20includes%20other%20amenities%20of%20the%20existing%20Vande%20Bharat%20trains%20such%20as%20fully%20air-conditioned%20coaches%2C%20automatic%20plug%20doors%2C%20and%20mobile%20charging%20sockets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20officials%2C%20the%20train%20symbolises%20India's%20commitment%20to%20bridging%20geographical%20and%20economic%20gaps%2C%20reported%20PTI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20train%20marks%20a%20significant%20step%20towards%20completing%20the%20272-km%20USBRL%20(Udhampur-Srinagar-Baramulla%20Rail%20Link)%C2%A0project%20-%20aimed%20at%20connecting%20the%20Kashmir%20valley%20to%20the%20broader%20Indian%20Railway%20network.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1737793380000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-01%2Fjjdevta_vande-bharat-_625x300_25_January_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fvideo-vande-bharats-successful-trial-run-on-worlds-highest-rail-bridge-in-jammu-and-kashmir-7555622%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20a%20boost%20to%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir's%20rail%20connectivity%2C%20the%20India%20Railways%20on%20Saturday%20successfully%20conducted%20the%20first%20trial%20run%20of%20the%20specially%20designed%20Vande%20Bharat%20Express%20train.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fvideo-vande-bharats-successful-trial-run-on-worlds-highest-rail-bridge-in-jammu-and-kashmir-7555622%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3