0Officer%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20small%20village%20of%20Aruapalli%20in%20Odisha%2C%20Jhili%20Rout%20cradles%20her%20newborn%20with%20relief%20and%20gratitude.%20As%20a%20mother%20of%20two%2C%20her%20journey%20through%20her%20recent%20pregnancy%20underscores%20the%20profound%20challenges%20faced%20by%20families%20in%20rural%20India%2C%20where%20access%20to%20essential%20healthcare%20can%20often%20seem%20like%20a%20distant%20dream.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20Jhili%20(25)%2C%20whose%20family%20of%20eight%20struggles%20with%20an%20unstable%20income%2C%20healthcare%20costs%20could%20have%20been%20an%20insurmountable%20burden.%20Her%20husband%E2%80%99s%20modest%20earnings%20as%20an%20agricultural%20labourer%20often%20run%20dry%20meeting%20the%20family%E2%80%99s%20needs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecalling%20her%20first%20experience%20with%20antenatal%20care%2C%20she%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CFive%20years%20back%2C%20when%20I%20was%20pregnant%20with%20my%20first%20child%2C%20I%20received%20two%20ultrasound%20scans%20that%20cost%20me%20Rs%201%2C600.%20My%20husband%20requested%20%3Cem%3Esahukar%20%3C%2Fem%3E(employer)%20to%20lend%20him%20this%20amount.%20For%20families%20like%20us%2C%20sparing%20so%20much%20amount%20is%20not%20easy%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%222400846096%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Jhili%20was%20able%20to%20monitor%20her%20second%20pregnancy%20closely%20without%20the%20financial%20strain.%20Thanks%20to%20the%20Ganjam%20District%20Administration%E2%80%99s%20initiative%2C%20she%20was%20offered%20up%20to%20three%20ultrasound%20scans%20for%20free%20of%20cost.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22